**Story**
Once upon a time. in a forest. there lived a monkey who resided on a jamoon (berry) tree, which was on then branks of a river, in the same forest, there lived a cocodrile and his wife.......r
One day, the cocodrile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree. the kindhearted monkey offered  him some fruits. The crocodrile came back the next day for more fruits, as he loved then. As days passed by, the crocodile and the monkey became good friends


